s/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"511c882b48dbe81dea01baf8b9275d7098ceab35","tid":423354,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T08:38:02.000Z","msg":"真係羡煞旁人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a59b10307207e1aa84741caa2c6caeee3d1c56c8","tid":423354,"uid":1248,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T08:38:25.000Z","msg":"加泰幾日vs香港79日⭕️<br />\n加泰五百年vs香港幾年❌"},{"pid":"336a6f98df5de807b11c733ad28dbedd796fc7d2","tid":423354,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T08:43:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇完人地望返香港坐係度今天我<br />\n同怕激嬲共產黨真係得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以前好多中國人避左中共逃到世界各地<br />\n如同個唔夠文明嘅政權鬥<br />\n送死嘅多<br />\n有命嘅都入獄、襟錮<br />\n最慘連家人都受罪<br />\n<br />\n所以最後香港人咪唯有唱今天我自high<br />\n因為都無乜其他出路了<br />\n敢唱歌<br />\n至少代表仲有思想靈魂<br />\n未係完全做左奴隸<br />\n<br />\n遲下可能連唱今天我都會比人拉去坐監<br />\n到時要改為做手語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"402a733a62f26482e3cc302a024aaa25ed59e13e","tid":423354,"uid":39177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T08:47:25.000Z","msg":"當年見到雙學放飯入政總,即刻決定唔再去金鐘"},{"pid":"7d9fc97db4218a833bd066fdc24931101d04b803","tid":423354,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T08:53:31.000Z","msg":"加泰酒店唔做西警生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n俾著香港班生意佬肯定揾錢至上"},{"pid":"b5ebc119316aa725f022f85322671bd106c489db","tid":423354,"uid":106641,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T09:05:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇完人地望返香港坐係度今天我<br />\n同怕激嬲共產黨真係得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啱啱仲要睇到香港同加泰差唔多人口 人地為左獨立出成百萬人 香港就<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n加泰隆尼亞<br />\n人口： 752.3 萬 (2016 年)<br />\n<br />\n香港<br />\n人口： 734.7 萬 (2016 年)</blockquote><br />\n人種問題</blockquote><br />\n冇錯，見到好多人講埋講埋咁多原因，理由真係晒鬼氣，最根本原因就係人種嘅分別"},{"pid":"4c4c971800670d27bad80f302a14be577fdd57d6","tid":423354,"uid":7529,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T09:06:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇完人地望返香港坐係度今天我<br />\n同怕激嬲共產黨真係得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人地坐喺度唱今天我打飛機，你坐喺度留言笑佢地唔敢做呃正評打飛機，其實大家都係冇圍到香港警察總部，不用分那麼細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4188fa37fee3139c74103a524b48ac5b1ab36a0e","tid":423354,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T10:25:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18c53a091d9b4502425f34a265aa4ebde512c413","tid":423354,"uid":17822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T11:22:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>包圍之後有冇好似我地包圍政總咁讓一條路出黎俾警察返工放工?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人道立場送食物喎<br />\n開路比人入政總返工放工喎<br />\n仲要明明傾撚完話寸步不讓 轉個頭就有人私自釋出善意 阻都阻唔撚到 屌你老母臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以我上面咪話個夜一定贏如果唔係果2個校長出黎。<br />\n其實我果陣心諗：屌我又唔係hku cu人,關我撚事咩<br />\n比佢地運物資都冇用<br />\n如果係衝根本阻唔到我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9069a28b59a2cb86152e269a5b8b5745caa4ce6","tid":423354,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T11:34:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29e98f5a075aadfd4b93630fe012cd5a0b96f0f1","tid":423354,"uid":73722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T11:40:19.000Z","msg":"我覺得要搞清楚既係香港班狗比佢地更無人性，為份工，上頭叫你開槍，你會唔會話辭職"},{"pid":"fa8bf4f5487fe5d68cbd09171b36808fe68c8fb1","tid":423354,"uid":25771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"