/span>"},{"pid":"ea20408f7d2a7ca7f2045138f3dcb83badff6fca","tid":423354,"uid":71315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T00:32:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港人係有種心魔<br />\n唔希望捲入更大/更不可預計既危機當中 <br />\n搞雨革已經諗定點抽身退場 點樣保持完好咁還返個場比政府 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有班人係太斯文有禮 太講道德原則<br />\n往往道德標準越黎越高 可以做既事只會越少<br />\n當政府唔理你/傾唔成個陣 呢班人就企左係度陣腳大亂<br />\n有流血衝突/武力衝擊爆玻璃 已經想割蔗 想求饒<br />\n假如有人係意外中身亡 佢地就只會係度追究責任 Blame the victim</blockquote><br />\n講得好"},{"pid":"5a38391c7738017475d7e576ad3437d8c1400326","tid":423354,"uid":71315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T00:36:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>包圍之後有冇好似我地包圍政總咁讓一條路出黎俾警察返工放工?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人道立場送食物喎<br />\n開路比人入政總返工放工喎<br />\n仲要明明傾撚完話寸步不讓 轉個頭就有人私自釋出善意 阻都阻唔撚到 屌你老母臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n諗起都覺得好笑，<br />\n香港人真係除左番工之外無野岩"},{"pid":"6eeb84fb02e93e9c03a3613f85854206b551c15b","tid":423354,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T01:05:06.000Z","msg":"西班牙有民主+歐盟背景都咁惡<br />\n中國只會更加殘忍<br />\n用加泰同香港比果班係咪傻左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf690667c0d2547e6b81d937a4abe09c8c38f79f","tid":423354,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T01:52:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Oct5近期活躍五毛<br />\nJR<br />\n三色貓<br />\n民國復興<br />\n熱血藍絲<br />\nbb chu<br />\nRedbaron<br />\n阿古路<br />\nnewlife<br />\n優美開始<br />\n人見人愛<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"6634d5de76ad1936bc340f5ea41f2c78cabce701","tid":423354,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T03:19:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcf07f5cae38f82ee76ad404c30976400809b92e","tid":423354,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017